name: Trash Been
description:
Hello! 

This is my very first game, which I created for 2 days without much Unity experience. But with invaluable help from people from the Official Unity Discord! 

Music: Dead Cells - Collector's Theme (composed and performed by Yoann Laulan)

Assets: FreePik.com (Royalty Free with paid subscription)

Based on Platform Template by Thomas Brush.   Thomas Brush.

PLEASE GIVE ME SOME HONEST FEEDBACK IN THE COMMENTS SECTION OR ON DISCORD Gogo#1266! 
Example of feedback I am looking for: 

  • Was it fun? 
  • Was it hard?
  • Were the controlls annoying?
  • Did you feel like finishing the game?
  • Was it memorable?
  • Did you feel like replaying?
  •  Were there any bugs?
